Titolo: Attack of the Killer Tomatoes (1986 video game)

Anno: 1986

Descrizione: Attack of the Killer Tomatoes is a computer game released in 1986 for the Sinclair Spectrum, Amstrad CPC and MSX.  It is based on the 1978 comedy film of the same name.
The player takes control of Wimp Plasbot, who works in a tomato puree plant, and must rid the plant of the mutated killer tomatoes, referred to in the title.